- Impact on Data Interpretation: The work had a profound influence on how data was perceived and utilized, moving away from purely textual descriptions to visual analysis.
- Contribution to Statistical Graphics: Playfair’s development of visual data methods laid the groundwork for modern statistical graphics and data visualization practices.{\textless}br{\textgreater}{\textless}br{\textgreater}Publication Details:{\textless}br{\textgreater}
